data.description: Take a look at this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath home, Fully fenced in a HUGE CORNER LOT!! perfect for anyone looking for a primary residence or investment property. The spacious floor plan offers a formal Living Room and a formal Dining Room, a Large Family Room, and an Open Kitchen with plenty of cabinet space and counter space. The Main bedroom occupies one side of the house and the 3 other bedrooms are on the opposite side of the house. The Master Bath offers a Dual Sink Vanity, a Garden Tub, and a Separate Shower. There is a separate Interior Laundry Room with easy access to the garage. Enjoy the OPEN PATIO overlooking more than a 1/4 acre lot with plenty of room to build a Swimming Pool! Best of all, you will enjoy the benefits of living in a Natural Reserve and a Resort Style Community. The Community offers 24hr Gated Security, 3 Pools, 2 fitness centers, Daily Fitness Classes, and Social Activities, a Sunset Pool Grille and so much more. Shopping and restaurants at your fingertips and private access to Lake Toho through a state-of-the-art boat lift and ramp. Come live the Florida lifestyle!!!
